<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《菊》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七月篱下花悬空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举杯小酌花色浓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清寒自居靖元故</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯有寄情散瓣中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200823/68a31d3616514d27acde878fd4b7aa68.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
