➜【星连文学社】维港泊人（香港）：《枯叶》
http://www.sohu.com/a/414529598_100115135	40984
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200823/25d46143a07c4cad86ab59cb246cd3cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《枯叶》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/维港泊人（香港）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恰似花朵的丫环</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一生陪嫁左右</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好想为你讨回公道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一片跌落尘埃的枯叶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">追随在风里雨里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寂寞于掌声之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生时尽翠，枯作春泥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你沉默，忠诚，始终不渝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可有谁？为你流过心疼的眼泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假如这世界选举最美的无名英雄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我要献花致敬的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正是你！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（23，08，2020）</strong></p>
